    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/7f119bd1bd7970c9d3d37887339f10ec.poster.avif?t=1758430196\" width=520 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/7f119bd1bd7970c9d3d37887339f10ec.webm?t=1758430196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong> Idle Catfarmia是一款放置式农场管理游戏。帮助猫妖管理资源，种植，收获和管理农场。农场增长得越高效，您的钱包也会越来越丰厚。偶尔出现在农场上的不受欢迎的访客需要展示您的点击技巧。 </strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/dbcecdf591f3280690e48f5b8e546684.poster.avif?t=1758430196\" width=578 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/dbcecdf591f3280690e48f5b8e546684.webm?t=1758430196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/dbcecdf591f3280690e48f5b8e546684.mp4?t=1758430196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>24种各种不同的资源和自由的资源布局</li></ul>资源分为三种类型：植物，动物和矿物，每种类型都提供8种资源。您可以在您想要的位置布置资源，并根据布置方式获得额外的生产奖励。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/0f27484f240e680917999527e049da86.poster.avif?t=1758430196\" width=578 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/0f27484f240e680917999527e049da86.webm?t=1758430196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/0f27484f240e680917999527e049da86.mp4?t=1758430196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5种猫妖</li></ul>五种猫妖将帮助生产资源。召唤高级猫妖以提高整个农场的生产力。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/fb76897fa88cf81941000c5a4346789c.poster.avif?t=1758430196\" width=578 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/fb76897fa88cf81941000c5a4346789c.webm?t=1758430196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399080/extras/fb76897fa88cf81941000c5a4346789c.mp4?t=1758430196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>由玩家改变的成长平衡</li></ul>农场不会以固定数值增长。根据适当资源的更换和有效布局，农场的增长速度会有所不同。您可以选择慢慢管理农场或高效管理。",
